props.darkThemeId: Id of the dark theme. You could create and publish dark themes at [My Maps](https://lbsyun.baidu.com/apiconsole/custommap), and get themes' Ids.
props.enableScrollWheelZoom: Whether allows to use mouse wheel to zoom the map or not.
props.maxZoom: Max zoom level of the map.
props.minZoom: Min zoom level of the map.
props.mapType: Type of the map (Normal map, earth map or satellite map).
props.trafficOn: Whether turns on the traffic layer or not.
